code:
sequenceDiagram
    participant AlbumPage
    participant AlbumDAO
    participant ImageDAO
    participant CTX
    participant TemplateEngine

    AlbumPage ->>+ AlbumDAO: new AlbumDAO(Education_LMS_Portal)
    AlbumPage ->> AlbumDAO: get(Education_ContentCDN)
    alt album exists
        AlbumDAO -->> AlbumPage: Optional<Album>
        AlbumPage ->>+ ImageDAO: new ImageDAO(Education_StudentDB)
        AlbumPage ->> ImageDAO: getAlbumImages(Education_GradeSync)
        ImageDAO -->> AlbumPage: images
        AlbumPage -->> CTX: setVariable(Education_GradeSync)
        AlbumPage -->> CTX: setVariable(Education_GradeSync)
        AlbumPage -->> CTX: setVariable(Education_LMS_Portal)
        AlbumPage -->> TemplateEngine: process(Education_GradeSync)
    else album does not exist
        AlbumDAO -->> AlbumPage: Optional.empty(Education_StudentDB)
        AlbumPage --> AlbumPage: response.sendError(Education_GradeSync)
    end
